OL,3,CPPS to consider any basis for appeal
OL,4,Cagainst Oliver MacCormack sentence
OL,6,FMacCormack was sentenced to seven
OL,7,Fyears, with half to be served in jail
OL,8,Fand the other half on licence.
OL,10,FHowever, the time he has already spent
OL,11,Fin prison will be factored in. He has
OL,12,Fbeen in custody since May 2022.
OL,14,FSinn Fein's justice spokeswoman
OL,15,FDeirdre Hargey said she had written to
OL,16,Fthe PPS asking them to "consider
OL,17,Fappealing the sentence imposed on a
OL,18,Fsex offender who preyed on vulnerable
OL,19,Fwomen".
