OL,3,CPPS to consider any basis for appeal
OL,4,Cagainst Oliver MacCormack sentence
OL,6,F"In this case, the sentencing remarks
OL,7,Fwill be carefully considered to
OL,8,Festablish whether there is any legal
OL,9,Fbasis to refer the sentence to the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,12,F"We will keep the victims and family
OL,13,Fof the deceased victim informed of the
OL,14,Foutcome of these considerations."
OL,16,FMacCormack, whose address was given as
OL,17,FMaghaberry Prison, was sentenced in
OL,18,Frelation to nine victims. One has
OL,19,Fsince died of sepsis because of
OL,20,Fintravenous drug use.
